#. <section class="sutta" id="sn5.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn5.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn5.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Bhikkhunīvagga"
msgstr "1. Nuns"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn5.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Vijayāsutta"
msgstr "4. With Vijayā"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.4:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn5.4:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho vijayā bhikkhunī pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā … pe …"
msgstr "Then the nun Vijayā robed up in the morning …"

msgctxt "sn5.4:1.3"
msgid "aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle divāvihāraṃ nisīdi."
msgstr "and sat at the root of a tree for the day’s meditation."

msgctxt "sn5.4:1.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā vijayāya bhikkhuniyā bhayaṃ chambhitattaṃ lomahaṃsaṃ "
"uppādetukāmo samādhimhā cāvetukāmo yena vijayā bhikkhunī tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā vijayaṃ bhikkhuniṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then Māra the Wicked, wanting to make the nun Vijayā feel fear, terror, and "
"goosebumps, wanting to make her fall away from immersion, went up to her and "
"addressed her in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.131"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.4:2.1"
msgid "“Daharā tvaṃ rūpavatī,"
msgstr "“You’re so young and beautiful,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.4:2.2"
msgid "ahañca daharo susu;"
msgstr "and I’m a youth in my prime."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.4:2.3"
msgid "Pañcaṅgikena turiyena,"
msgstr "Come, my lady, let us enjoy"

#. <br>
#. VAR: ehayyebhiramāmase”ti → ehi ayye ramāmaseti (si) | ehayyebhiramāmhaseti (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn5.4:2.4"
msgid "ehayyebhiramāmase”ti."
msgstr "the music of a five-piece band.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.287"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.4:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho vijayāya bhikkhuniyā etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then the nun Vijayā thought:"

msgctxt "sn5.4:3.2"
msgid "“ko nu khvāyaṃ manusso vā amanusso vā gāthaṃ bhāsatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Who’s speaking this verse, a human or a non-human?”"

msgctxt "sn5.4:3.3"
msgid "Atha kho vijayāya bhikkhuniyā etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then she thought:"

msgctxt "sn5.4:3.4"
msgid ""
"“māro kho ayaṃ pāpimā mama bhayaṃ chambhitattaṃ lomahaṃsaṃ uppādetukāmo "
"samādhimhā cāvetukāmo gāthaṃ bhāsatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“This is Māra the Wicked, wanting to make me feel fear, terror, and "
"goosebumps, wanting to make me fall away from immersion!”"

msgctxt "sn5.4:3.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho vijayā bhikkhunī “māro ayaṃ pāpimā” iti viditvā māraṃ pāpimantaṃ "
"gāthāhi paccabhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then Vijayā, knowing that this was Māra the Wicked, replied to him in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.4:4.1"
msgid "“Rūpā saddā rasā gandhā,"
msgstr "“Sights, sounds, tastes, smells,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.4:4.2"
msgid "phoṭṭhabbā ca manoramā;"
msgstr "and touches so delightful."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.4:4.3"
msgid "Niyyātayāmi tuyheva,"
msgstr "I hand them right back to you, Māra,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.4:4.4"
msgid "māra nāhaṃ tenatthikā."
msgstr "for I have no use for them."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.4:5.1"
msgid "Iminā pūtikāyena,"
msgstr "This body is foul,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.4:5.2"
msgid "bhindanena pabhaṅgunā;"
msgstr "decaying and fragile."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.4:5.3"
msgid "Aṭṭīyāmi harāyāmi,"
msgstr "I’m horrified and repelled by it,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.4:5.4"
msgid "kāmataṇhā samūhatā."
msgstr "and I’ve eradicated sensual craving."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.4:6.1"
msgid "Ye ca rūpūpagā sattā,"
msgstr "There are beings in the realm of luminous form,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: arūpaṭṭhāyino → āruppaṭhāyino (bj, pts2) | arūpabhāgino (s1-3) | āruppaṭṭhāyino (pts1)
msgctxt "sn5.4:6.2"
msgid "ye ca arūpaṭṭhāyino;"
msgstr "others established in the formless,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.4:6.3"
msgid "Yā ca santā samāpatti,"
msgstr "and also those peaceful attainments:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.4:6.4"
msgid "sabbattha vihato tamo”ti."
msgstr "I’ve destroyed the darkness regarding all of them.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.4:7.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ vijayā bhikkhunī”ti dukkhī dummano "
"tatthevantaradhāyīti."
msgstr ""
"Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The nun Vijayā knows me!” miserable and "
"sad, vanished right there."
